node.text:
Watch how my facial hair has evolved over the years and how I use @braun_global’s new Series 7 both as a tool of self-expression and to manage my desired look on a daily basis! Well-groomed stubble or clean-shaven, whatever look you desire the Series 7 is here to help you #SayItWithAShave

Follow this link (https://bit.ly/3k22n28) to learn more about the Series 7 and comment below with the funniest moment of your shaving journey! Ad

#BraunUK #SayItWithAShave

node.text:
Found a new piece of equipment at the gym today, it was called a Thread-mil. I’m pretty sure it’s for chest 👌🏼

Wearing my favourite X-Line tank from @RISE 🚀they are on final sale so once they are gone that’s it! Use code: MARINO to support this guy right here and get 10% off 👊🏼

node.text:
𝐖𝐄 𝐀𝐑𝐄 𝐋𝐀𝐔𝐍𝐂𝐇𝐈𝐍𝐆 𝐀 𝐂𝐎𝐀𝐂𝐇𝐈𝐍𝐆 𝐀𝐏𝐏 🚀 For a LONG time now I have been wanting to offer more in terms of training & nutrition and share our 17+ years of experience with you and now I finally can 💪🏼 (swipe right to see us before the XP)

This is NOT your normal cookie cutter training plan! Every individual plan is custom made just for YOU, by myself for the guys and by Domi for the girls 💪🏼

Here are just a few of the many features!
✓ Personalised workout programs customized to your goals, preferences & physical ability
✓ Adaptive programming to allow for continuous progressive overload
✓ Workout log and progress tracker
✓ Video demonstrations of all exercises
✓ Tips and cues to optimize every workout
✓ In depth coaching to maximize your results
✓ Customized, flexible meal plans with IIFYM support
✓ Support for all diets, eating habits and food preferences
✓ Hundreds of nutritionally complete recipes designed to maximize energy and satiety levels
✓ Non-restrictive meal plans which accommodate and readjust to include any unplanned snacks or meals, including a database of restaurant options
✓ Access to a community support group
✓ Ongoing email & chat support

We will be constantly updating and adding new features to ensure you are always receiving the latest cutting-edge features as well as continuously updating you with the latest advancements in training and nutrition studies!

Follow the link in my story or bio to sign up for an exclusive discount when the app launches 🚀

node.text:
What you think you look like getting out of the pool vs what you actually look like 🙃

Tag a mate who thinks they’re too cool ⤵️

#funny #pool #reality #comedy #summer

Bodyweight CORE burner 🔥

Never underestimate the power of floor ab exercises. They can put the most advanced of lifters in their place!

1. Leg lifts 12-15 reps
2. One leg lifts 10 reps each side
3. Side crunch 12 reps each side
4. Double crunch 10 reps
5. Leg circles 10 reps
🔴Rest 90 seconds
🟢Repeat 4-5 times

*You can do this workout as a circuit or each exercise one by one for 3 sets 💪🏼 give it a go and feel the burn

📍 @acrosuites

node.text: don’t worry everybody I’m working on ending global warming by simply being very, very cool

Dumbbell ONLY arm workout 💪🏼

Build those biceps & triceps only using DBs with this effective superset workout!

1. Curl & twist 3x10-12 into ⤵️
2. Skull crushers x tricep press 3x10-12 each
3. Seated hammer curl 3x8-10 into ⤵️
4. Overhead extensions 3x12-15
5. Spider curls 3x12-15 into ⤵️
6. Kick backs 3x10-12 each

This one will leave you with an outrageous pump guaranteed 👌🏼 Give it a go if you’re short on time or only have limited equipment available 👊🏼

Gym - @asanafitnessclub
